txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Large finger bones from the Dead in the eastern Lone-lands. Bring them to Hana the Young at Ost Guruth.
'It is good to know that there are still some in this world willing to help each other.\n\n'Thank you.'
'The Lore-master in Brown bid me collect these bones, else the dead Men whence they came dance themselves back to health.'
Hana the Young at Ost Guruth desires large finger bones from the Dead found in the eastern Lone-lands.
Deliver the large finger bones to Hana the Young at Ost Guruth
You accepted a task from Hana the Young to acquire large finger bones from the Dead in the eastern Lone-lands. You can find Hana the Young within Ost Guruth.
Wanted: Large finger bones from the Dead in the eastern Lone-lands.
